videos.description: De'Aaron Fox drives the lane and gets Jamal Murray to reach while finishing the shot plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Fox catches Murray reaching, finishes and-1) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fox catches Murray reaching, finishes and-1

videos.description: Jamal Murray drives down the lane and emphatically flushes the dunk with one hand.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Murray hammers one on Bagley) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Murray hammers one on Bagley

videos.description: Kings first-round pick Tyrese Haliburton knocks down two, big-time 3-pointers late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Haliburton hits two huge 3s for Kings) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Haliburton hits two huge 3s for Kings

videos.description: The Nuggets turn it over with under five seconds remaining leading to Harrison Barnes missing the dunk, but Buddy Hield tips it in for the win.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Hield beats the buzzer with tip-in) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hield beats the buzzer with tip-in

videos.description: The Nuggets and Kings go back and forth in overtime, eventually ending in a Nuggets turnover and a Buddy Hield tip-in at the buzzer to win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Kings win on Hield’s tip-in for wild OT finish) 2020/12/23 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Kings win on Hield's tip-in for wild OT finish

videos.description: Nikola Jokic records the triple-double with 29 points, 15 rebounds and 14 assists, however the Nuggets would fall to the Kings in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Jokic starts season with triple-double in heartbreaking Nuggets loss) 2020/12/23 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Jokic starts season with triple-double in heartbreaking Nuggets loss
